item.description:
This concert is part of a series during Yankee Homecoming week in Newburyport. These concerts are FREE and very well-attended. Please bring a chair or blanket for seating. THIS IS A SHARED EVENT with other meetup groups.

MUSIC: begins at 7:30

WE WILL MEETUP: in front of The Firehouse Center For The Arts - by the bench with the shadey tree. I'll have either a meetup.com sign or wear my meetup pin.... My contact info will be remitted to all 'yes' RSVP prior. *** Parking can be tight -especially during Yankee Homecoming. So, please make sure to allow for that timewise.....

**This is an all-outdoor event. RAIN CANCELS. I will update depending on weather condition. I will add my conact info as the sdate get closer.

Music begins @ 7:30
(www. jamesmontgomery.com)
